Copyright
=========

   The original Post (up to V1.7) came from Adrian Aylward which was
slightly improved by Robert Poole (V1.86enh, plus a bugfix). Adrian did
an excellent job and without his work Post V2.00 would not exist.
Therefore I included his name although my version of post has almost
nothing to do with his work as you can see browsing through the sources.
I also kept Poole's name because it was actually Post V1.86enh I started
with. But please keep in mind that the copyright of Post V2.00 and later
fully belongs to me (See @{"Author" Link "Author"}).

   The GUI designed with GadToolsBox ((C) Jan van den Baard).


@EndNode

