License
=======

   Distribution is allowed in all forms, such as BB systems, floppy or
compact disks, and ftp sites. Post may be freely distributed if:

   * no  more  then a  reasonable  fee is charged  for  copying or
     down-loading.

   * no file in this distribution is changed, added or removed.

   * the distribution is not part of a commercial product. In case you
     want to use Post in a commercial product get in contact with me
     (See @{"Author" Link "Author"}).

   Post is Giftware, it is not Public Domain! If you use Post longer
than two weeks you have to send a gift to me (See @{"Author" Link "Author"})!

   As the source is included everyone has the chance to improve Post.
But please do not distribute your own version of Post 'cause this will
end up in a chaos. Please send me your suggestions, improvements or
whatever.  I'll try to implement them and take your name in the history
and acknowledgements. And of course you do not have to send a fee if you
help to improve Post!


@EndNode

