@EndNode

@Node "ARexx-Interface" "Post.guide/ARexx-Interface"
@Next "Menus of Post"
@Prev "The Options Window"
@Toc "Usage"

ARexx-Interface
===============

   Post supports many ARexx commands (they are not case sensitive):

   * Window functions: OPENWINDOW, CLOSEWINDOW, WINDOWTOFRONT,
     WINDOWTOBACK, ACTIVATEWINDOW, ZIPWINDWOW, CHANGEWINDOWBOX left,
     top, width, height

   * Screen functions: SCREENTOFRONT, SCREENTOBACK, CUSTOMSCREEN,
     PUBSCREEN pubscrname

   * Scroll functions: LEFT n, RIGHT n, UP n, DOWN n

   * OPEN file, RUN file, LOADFONT font, CLEAR, INTERRUPT, KILL

   * Page control functions: NEXTPAGE, PREVIOSPAGE, GOTOPAGE n

   * Miscellaneous: QUIT, GETSTATUS, SETOPTS optfile

   Every ARexx command not listed above is sent to the interpreter.
Please see `PostRexxDemo.rexx' for more information.


@EndNode

