Support
=======

   First of all: I am afraid I do not have enough time for Post! And
nothing and nobody is perfect and maybe Post will never be bug free.
But I will try to improve it and upload new versions to aminet. You can
also ask me for help (best via email, please preface your header with
`POST'). But as I have to finish my studies please don't mail bomb me
with a problem you might solve yourself by thinking it over for a few
more minutes :-)

   If you found a bug please be sure it can be reproduced and include a
detailed description (KS/WB version, CPU type, running commodities and
other utilities ...)


@EndNode

